    <div class="content"><p>Also, the "flypast of Earth" in Crossroads clearly showed North America, but the flypast of "Earth" in Revelations did not. You can see the screencaps side-by-side <a href="http://www.lisapaitzspindler.com/blog/2008/06/18/nothing-but-the-radioactive-rain-sir/" rel="nofollow">here.</a></p>
