    <h3 class="title"><a href="/battlestar/one-earth-or-two-more-data-more-astronomy#comment-6795" class="active">I used to use scientific</a></h3>    <div class="submitted">Submitted by Dustin (not verified) on Thu, 2009-01-22 08:35.</div>
