  <div class="comment">
    <h3 class="title"><a href="/battlestar/one-earth-or-two-more-data-more-astronomy#comment-6905" class="active">Red Dwarf: Back to Earth</a></h3>    <div class="submitted">Submitted by Anonymous (not verified) on Thu, 2009-01-29 10:10.</div>
    <div class="content"><p>Red Dwarf is returning to the screens and even that bunch of clowns look like they'll &lt; href="http://www.guardian.co.uk/media/2009/jan/27/red-dwarf-cast-reunited"&gt;find Earth</a>. Unless, some stray god has sneaked into our universe, stolen it, and replaced it with an exact duplicate. But, hey. That's showbiz.</p>
</div>
